id":"A-UnNdvvRri0485OwDXWDQ","children":[]}]},{"id":"244","parent":"234","text":"MANEJO CONSERVADOR","guid":"xR7AJdU7RMWmmdiTLmV8DQ","children":[{"id":"245","parent":"244","text":"NO forzar ingesta","guid":"XMsMiUyOT4WXrkWtr5ldow","children":[]},{"id":"246","parent":"244","text":"NO jeringuillas a presión + NO pajitas","guid":"Cmq049EzRwWRTeFAg15M7A","children":[]},{"id":"247","parent":"244","text":"Consistencia HOMOGÉNEA (purés)","guid":"yE-pVo04TPmDMtDoFW1oxA","children":[]},{"id":"248","parent":"244","text":"ESPESANTES (sémola, tapioca o comerciales)","guid":"UjpYFd5USGWJ1AzDXFDrLw","children":[]},{"id":"249","parent":"244","text":"CONSISTENCIAS: NÉCTAR < MIEL < PUDDING","guid":"vz1E3BwdSXiHjrpLbUwobg","children":[]},{"id":"250","parent":"244","text":"GELATINAS + aguas gelificadas","guid":"MYnPDYGZQa6mdQnR-vXbZA","children":[]}]},{"id":"251","parent":"234","text":"POSTURA DEGLUCIÓN","guid":"Pmjqf7kXRIS_Jm9h8zxbcQ","children":[{"id":"252","parent":"251","text":"SENTADO + espalda recta","guid":"VEOTBFzhRV-vu8w0xHMoSA","children":[]},{"id":"253","parent":"251","text":"CABEZA LIGERAMENTE FLEXIONADA adelante (chin-tuck)","guid":"tHxN0TvqRkKGT5pTXvGFVg","children":[]},{"id":"254","parent":"251","text":"Encamado → incorporar máximo","guid":"iX4gVoLMS4OmDVhVAtDVQQ","children":[]},{"id":"255","parent":"251","text":"NUNCA alimentar a persona TUMBADA","guid":"V_-pA2zBTNSApAgrKDoHvQ","children":[]},{"id":"256","parent":"251","text":"Post-ingesta → incorporado 30-40 min","guid":"JB0cc3i4QJC0MI_-PJkgFg","children":[]}]}]},{"id":"257","parent":"209","text":"NUTRICIÓN ENTERAL","guid":"pmjHr0hPQCKo9CH4JDNmRg","children":[{"id":"258","parent":"257","text":"Indicación → tubo digestivo funcional + oral imposible","guid":"OUL7mZzGQ3SO_0nbELdKsw","children":[]},{"id":"259","parent":"257","text":"VÍAS → SNG o PEG","guid":"7236NEmmRGWM6hvVaqsoVA","children":[]},{"id":"260","parent":"257","text":"Incorporar 30-45° + mantener ≥1h post","guid":"l2fPfZ5ITuaImDdTR0CgMw","children":[]},{"id":"261","parent":"257","text":"Verificar posición sonda","guid":"8Ji11MoTTIKQjzZL294WIg","children":[]},{"id":"262","parent":"257","text":"Lavado 30-50 ml agua antes/después","guid":"WaWkr5mKTdelwgyIuaKiow","children":[]},{"id":"263","parent":"257","text":"MEDICAMENTOS POR SONDA","guid":"1-YYT8THRo6ygKvXbRlNYg","children":[{"id":"264","parent":"263","text":"NO mezclar con alimento","guid":"lrB-3maeSvqYwna-76862g","children":[]},{"id":"265","parent":"263","text":"NO mezclar varios fármacos entre sí","guid":"-bUp2SmDShODPPzFDxUoCg","children":[]},{"id":"266","parent":"263","text":"Preferir presentación líquida","guid":"C5CFbm1lQ1meBujpAXYWAA","children":[]},{"id":"267","parent":"263","text":"Triturar → polvo fino + 30 ml agua","guid":"sOdK31noQQaN88Jkoo0wQw","children":[]},{"id":"268","parent":"263","text":"Primero líquidos → luego sólidos","guid":"xkHB9o83Rhm4xzReqHOpSA","children":[]}]}]}]},{"id":"269","parent":"0","text":"Perlas Clínicas","guid":"NpUWXARXRzy75cPr6rnDeA","children":[{"id":"270","parent":"269","text":"Autonomía moral persiste aunque colapse la funcional → preguntar siempre antes de sustituir","guid":"3mNDf16EQMu4gm07Xt9J9Q","children":[]},{"id":"271","parent":"269","text":"OMS ≥65a → 150 min/sem aeróbico + fuerza ≥2 d/sem + equilibrio ≥3 d/sem si riesgo caída","guid":"gAG6N37gQrufdFF6TePpdw","children":[]},{"id":"272","parent":"269","text":"Paseo post-comida → doble beneficio (higiene sueño + estimulación) → sustituye 0.5 tableta zolpidem","guid":"w-zr492cRmajumj5-1pQGg","children":[]},{"id":"273","parent":"269","text":"Uñas de pies en LÍNEA RECTA → previene onicocriptosis, puerta de entrada a celulitis en DM","guid":"d2bv-UKQQCixZ_ETSGyvUA","children":[]},{"id":"274","parent":"269","text":"VESTIDO → lado AFECTADO primero; DESVESTIDO → lado SANO primero","guid":"JR5ZPyl8TVGw4QRWA5sW_A","children":[]},{"id":"275","parent":"269","text":"TRANSFERENCIA → rodillas del cuidador bloquean las del paciente + espalda RECTA","guid":"XVeIv3KHRV6t5mW4d2stqQ","children":[]},{"id":"276","parent":"269","text":"Cambios posturales CADA 2h + inspección piel → pilar prevención UPP","guid":"5KnLaIvZTQityO4NmlIq_Q","children":[]},{"id":"277","parent":"269","text":"BASTÓN/muleta SIEMPRE en lado SANO (brazo de palanca)","guid":"Md38KGGTQT-jm6ZgZO0Hlw","children":[]},{"id":"278","parent":"269","text":"BZD y Z-drugs en AM → ↑caída + fractura + delirium (Beers) → higiene del sueño primero","guid":"cSmny4ExQAyBPEg1MGtqBQ","children":[]},{"id":"279","parent":"269","text":"DISFAGIA → chin-tuck + textura pudding/miel + incorporado 30-40min post-ingesta","guid":"qC3ldm3eSgiXxnWLPvNqFw","children":[]},{"id":"280","parent":"269","text":"Pérdida peso >7,5%/3m o >10%/6m = ALARMA → cribar con MNA","guid":"Gw3wj4S-RZWai5Wkhgky9Q","children":[]},{"id":"281","parent":"269","text":"Medicación por sonda: NUNCA mezclar fármacos; triturar, diluir 30 ml, lavar entre dosis","guid":"cCV_qSqITyuYoH1NFagDyA","children":[]},{"id":"282","parent":"269","text":"Referencias","guid":"FZJJRyBxTjC17rH9dWEX-g","children":[{"id":"283","parent":"282","text":"1. SEGG. Curso cuidadores PM dependencia. Tema 5: Promover la autonomía. Madrid; 2023. ISBN 978-84-09-47741-8.","guid":"VaY_hXq6QSC8ApfuL0y01Q","children":[]},{"id":"284","parent":"282","text":"2. SEGG. Idem. Tema 6: Actividad y ejercicio físico. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"2LT3sZvtQ_2iwFhIwundLg","children":[]},{"id":"285","parent":"282","text":"3. SEGG. Idem. Tema 7: Higiene personal. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"GpBjJkceRTytSDdEhJMTYg","children":[]},{"id":"286","parent":"282","text":"4. SEGG. Idem. Tema 8: Cuidado de la imagen personal. El vestido. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"iiO87TcZRqikOazhQ7CXWQ","children":[]},{"id":"287","parent":"282","text":"5. SEGG. Idem. Tema 9: Transferencias y movilizaciones. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"AxPeW9jySjOwxTmHtaKdGw","children":[]},{"id":"288","parent":"282","text":"6. SEGG. Idem. Tema 10: Descanso y sueño. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"9E0JeSp7Q1uJSS9OjBMJew","children":[]},{"id":"289","parent":"282","text":"7. SEGG. Idem. Tema 11: Alimentación y nutrición. Madrid; 2023.","guid":"iaagA_28SDWiL8GSe-8uAw","children":[]},{"id":"290","parent":"282","text":"8. CEAPAT. Productos de apoyo. Imserso. www.ceapat.es","guid":"qWblgk5IRbCILBbiZFlDhQ","children":[]},{"id":"291","parent":"282","text":"9. WHO. Guidelines on physical activity and sedentary behaviour. Geneva: WHO; 2020.","guid":"Ot_J5HTQQXCJei1mTqZhhg","children":[]}]}]}]},"node_count":291,"relations":[],"cross_references":[],"specialty":"Geriatría","folder":"Entidades clínicas/Geriatría/Cuidados-Domicilio","filename":"02-AVD-Cuidados-Basicos","id":"map_930","resolved_references":[],"title_raw":"02-AVD-Cuidados-Basicos"}